column4: NSLOCTEXT("[E20EDB97483DAFE9839BA0840D5B3274]", "7A73472943646647C7BA1C9B6B606512", "Oh no, if I don\'t do anything, it will dry up...")
NSLOCTEXT("[E20EDB97483DAFE9839BA0840D5B3274]", "DFA494D74BF138F7BF0427A0D1A8A69D", "It moved a little bit. Is this the mysterious plant everyone is talking about?")
NSLOCTEXT("[E20EDB97483DAFE9839BA0840D5B3274]", "73BC4FE44929114078322C89DF89B51C", "It\'s wilting. If I don\'t do anything, it\'ll die.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E20EDB97483DAFE9839BA0840D5B3274]", "6EC21792497461D11E872ABCB4C4E833", "By the way, do you like veggies?")
NSLOCTEXT("[E20EDB97483DAFE9839BA0840D5B3274]", "85BD8AB349008D9C14AD92AE6F5B491A", "Why are you asking me about veggies? Well?")
NSLOCTEXT("[E20EDB97483DAFE9839BA0840D5B3274]", "45B12DC64F6B4833EB3E9C974D91B2CC", "Anyone who likes veggies must be a nice guy.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E20EDB97483DAFE9839BA0840D5B3274]", "50095E544474F79AE76EE3910089B066", "Alright, I\'ve decided. I\'ll come with you!")
NSLOCTEXT("[E20EDB97483DAFE9839BA0840D5B3274]", "C672749F4755D931B8BBE49A5CD0DDCF", "What do you want me to do?")
NSLOCTEXT("[E20EDB97483DAFE9839BA0840D5B3274]", "4CD6AC9349568F41D0C932AC895B4C38", "Why don\'t you come to the city and help us!")
NSLOCTEXT("[E20EDB97483DAFE9839BA0840D5B3274]", "6142CBA94F9D5AC4352F6A9B7814C52A", "Alright, sounds good. I\'ve been here way too long.")
